Abstract = {{This paper presents new general formulas for calculating the magnetic
   force between inclined circular filaments placed in any desired
   position. We use two approaches to calculate the magnetic force, one
   based on Biot-Savart law and another based on the mutual inductance
   between these coils. All mathematical procedures are completely
   described to define coil positions that lead to relatively easy method
   for calculating the magnetic force between inclined circular filaments
   in any desired position. Two formulas obtained by the simple integration
   of different expressions in terms of complete elliptic integrals of the
   first and second kind give the same numerical results. The presented
   methods are understandable, numerically suitable and easy applicable for
   engineers and physicists. We validated the new formulas through a series
   of examples, which are presented here.}},
